de: Third Amendment to the Administration Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Single-Donor Trust Fund for Financial Sector Development Project in the Kyrgyz Republic (TF072607)  - 11-12-2017 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und der IBRD und IDA betreffend den "Kyrgyz Republic Financial Sector Development Project Single-Donor Trust Fund (No. TF072067)"
en: Third Amendment to the Administration Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Single-Donor Trust Fund for Financial Sector Development Project in the Kyrgyz Republic (TF072607)  - 11-12-2017 - Administration Agreement between the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (SECO) and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Kyrgyz Republic Financial Sector Development Project Single-Donor Trust Fund (No. TF072067)
fr: Third Amendment to the Administration Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Single-Donor Trust Fund for Financial Sector Development Project in the Kyrgyz Republic (TF072607)  - 11-12-2017 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et la BIRD et l'IDA concernant le "Kyrgyz Republic Financial Sector Development Project Single-Donor Trust Fund (No. TF072067)"
